1. The Eye
4. Contact
At Sāvatthī.
“Mendicants, eye contact is impermanent, perishing, and changing.
Ear contact,
nose contact,
tongue contact,
body contact,
and mind contact are impermanent, perishing, and changing.
Someone who has faith and confidence in these principles is called a follower by faith. …”


